msgid "These are the **basics**. For more details on settings and other bits included with the framework see :doc:`the static files howto </howto/static-files/index>` and the :doc:`the staticfiles reference </ref/contrib/staticfiles>`. :doc:`Deploying static files </howto/static-files/deployment>` discusses how to use static files on a real server."
